### Context

The dataset is extracted and pre-classified from VietAI FC6 Assignment 3 to be used with ImageDataGenerator.


### Content

I used shutil to copy the images into separated folders to be used with ImageDataGenerator, because the dataset is large and cannot fully convert to NumPy array with 16GB RAM.


### Acknowledgements

VietAI
